{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many things to see in these enchanted woods. Solve the puzzle, then explore with Miguel! Go say hi to everyone you meet, they might have a story to tell. Take a closer look at weird objects, they too can keep secrets. It\u2019s a new day full of new discoveries for our little shroom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A day with Miguel:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Miguel is a tiny mushroom! He lives with his mom in an enchanted forest, and now he's all grown up and should go to school! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploring new places:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Outside Mama Shroom's farm there's a whole forest! On Miguel's way to school, assemble the jigsaw puzzle and create a new area to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Forest Creatures:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The forest is full of different creatures. Miguel will meet many along the way. Will they be Shrooms, Blobs or\u2026 is that a Carrot reading a book? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The new acquaintances are friendly and can offer Miguel many fun quests to embark on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">School is big! Classes spread all over the forest. Explore, meet the teachers and discover a bit more of Miguel\u2019s world.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level 1 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1559100/2ff6bba5c17cee029de0c0f9203953e740a94d9f.jpg"},{"name":"Level 2 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1559100/c9608af0a32dd77a7a1ce7f87b43896536eeeded.jpg"},{"name":"Level 3 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1559100/fffac79a319c67c836111412bfcd58c2d220bac8.jpg"},{"name":"Level 4 Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1559100/1fb70bca349b387e0fdf1669633320cfdd19ea22.jpg"},{"name":"Level